# Google Cloud OAuth 2.0 client ID for Drive sync
# Create at: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# Type: Web application
# Authorized JS origin: https://ismarsh.github.io
# Authorized redirect URI: https://ismarsh.github.io/ohm/
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id-here.apps.googleusercontent.com

# Cloud Function URL for OAuth token exchange (enables persistent auth)
# Deploy from cloud-functions/token-exchange/, see gcp-oauth-token-exchange.md
# Omit to fall back to implicit OAuth (reconnect required after each refresh)
VITE_TOKEN_EXCHANGE_URL=https://us-central1-your-project.cloudfunctions.net/ohm-token-exchange
